        <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Venetian plaster and premium finishes.</h2>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Venetian plastering is a consistent feature — polished plaster in hallways, master suites, and feature walls. Sash window painting on the older properties, premium exterior render and masonry systems, and high-end interior decorating round out the work.</p>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">A clear written quote and a fixed price up front — exactly what this market expects.</p>
