    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 24px;">Working in Gerrards Cross</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">~15 minutes from base</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">A short run from Harefield via Denham and the A40. One of our closer affluent areas — no travel premium on the quote.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">High-spec ready</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Venetian plaster, premium paint systems, and exacting finishes — we bring the materials and standard the address calls for.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Discreet &amp; tidy</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Generous plots give ample access. We work cleanly and discreetly, with surfaces and features fully protected.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Insured &amp; qualified</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Fully insured and City &amp; Guilds qualified. No subcontractors — the same person quotes and works.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
